# PattayaPets operator workflow

Read `CLAUDE.md` first. Anything marked LOCKED there is non-negotiable.

## Deploy (canonical)

1. Edit source in `src/` only — never hand-edit `dist/`.
2. Run `npm run build` — must print valid JSON-LD for every page.
3. Push to `main` on GitHub — Cloudflare Pages auto-deploys.
4. Manual `wrangler pages deploy` is emergency fallback only.

## Git

- Commit only when Tim asks (or explicit "commit and push").
- Do not push unless asked.
- One focused change per commit when possible.

## After content changes

- Bump `updated` on edited pages.
- Directory listings: facts only until an anonymous visit; verdict stays pending.
- Run build before reporting done.

